    "created_at": "2015-09-23T15:06:48Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-09-23T15:06:48Z",
    "body": "I think the problem isn't that there are a lot of them, it's that they might leak over time and eventually you start seeing 'X will inform me that I have reached the maximum number of clients.' - this might _solely_ be a bug on the Slack app's end though. \n"
